    <h>a</h>
    <p><g>a</g>
        <en>his, her, its</en> is the third person singular <a
            href="?xx=nouns/possessive_determiners">possessive determiner</a>, related to the
        personal pronouns <a href="?gd=i">i</a>
        <en>she, her, it</en> and <a href="?gd=e">e</a>
        <en>he, him, it</en>.</p>
    <!--<p>cf. other uses of the particle <a href="?gd=a">a</a>.</p>-->
   
